decision_conditions:
&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Prior to the commencement of relevant works details, including
samples and mock ups where deemed necessary, of materials to be used
on the external surfaces of the building, boundary walls and ground
surfaces shall be submitted to and approved by the Local Planning
Authority, in writing. The development shall not be carried out
otherwise than in accordance with the details thus approved. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the external appearance of the building is
satisfactory and does not detract from the character and visual
amenity of the area.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;The proposed D1 space shall be built out to practical completion
prior to the occupation of the proposed residential units. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: In the interests of securing the community facility and
public benefits of this aspect of the proposed development.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;No panelised brick slip systems requiring vertical or horizontal
expansion joints shall be used on any of the building facades. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the external appearance of the building is
satisfactory and does not detract from the character and visual
amenity of the area.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Details of proposed signage to the community facility shall be
submitted to and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority
before the space is occupied.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the external appearance of the building is
satisfactory and does not detract from the character and visual
amenity of the area or the setting of the conservation area.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Prior to occupation of any part of the development, details of
external lighting to the building shall be submitted to and agreed by
the local planning authority. The lighting shall be implemented and
maintained thereafter prior to the occupation of the development. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: In order to prevent unnecessary light pollution to the
surrounding area, to safeguard amenity, highway safety and
biodiversity (in particular to prevent disturbance to bats).&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Prior to the occupation, the proposed development hereby approved
shall achieve Secure by Design accreditation. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To safeguard against potential crime and anti-social
behaviour.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;The development hereby permitted must be begun not later than the
expiration of three years from 25/09/2019.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: In order to comply with the provisions of the Town and
Country Planning Act 1990 as amended.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Detailed drawings/full particulars of the proposed development
showing the matters set out below must be submitted to and approved
by the Local Planning Authority, in writing, before the commencement
of relevant works. The development shall not be carried out otherwise
than in accordance with the details thus approved. a) Detailed
drawings of windows and doors, including sections and reveals b)
Detailed drawings of boundary treatments c) Detailed drawings of
balcony and roof terrace screening including manufactures details and
a sample of the screening 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the external appearance of the building is
satisfactory and does not detract from the character and visual
amenity of the area.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Works of construction shall be carried out in full accordance with
the Construction logistics plan approved as part of application
2020/1041, dated 24/09/20. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To avoid hazard and obstruction being caused to users of the
public highway and in the interest of public safety and amenity.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Works of construction shall be carried out in full accordance with
the Construction Method Statement approved as part of application
2020/1041, dated 24/09/20.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To avoid hazard and obstruction being caused to users of the
public highway and in the interest of public safety and amenity.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Works of construction shall be in full accordance with the details of
tree protection, approved as part of application 2020/1578 dated
03/06/20. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the carrying out of the approved development
does not result in any significant harm to this tree.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Detailed analysis of the location of the roots of the sycamore tree
in the neighbouring front garden at 52a Clapton Common shall be in
full accordance with the information approved as part of application
2020/1578 dated 03/06/20. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the carrying out of the approved development
does not result in any significant harm to this tree.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Design and construction details of the south western corner of the
proposed lower ground floor, access stairs and provision of any
hardstanding or parking bays as proposed shall be informed by the
intrusive root assessment of the sycamore tree, including appropriate
mitigation shall be in full accordance with the details approved as
part of application 2020/1578 dated 03/06/20. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the carrying out of the approved development
does not result in any significant harm to this tree.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Removal and appropriate disposal of Invasive Non-Native Species at
the site shall be in full accordance with the details approved as
part of application 2020/1578 dated 03/06/2020. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the Invasive Non-Native Species are properly
removed from the site and to prevent their spread.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Piling at the site shall be carried out in full accordance with the
Pre-Augering Document; Silent Piling Generic Method Statement; Health
Safety and Quality Document for Pile Installation dated 19/01/21 by
Berryrange; E0689-EEE-00-XX-DR-S-9107 RevP01;
E0689-EEE-00-GF-DR-S-1100 RevC01; E0689-EEE-00-B1-DR-S-1099 RevC02.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure the protection of identified third party owned
water mains and infrastructure beneath the site.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Prior to the first occupation of the development a delivery and
servicing management plan, including refuse, shall be submitted to
and approved in writing by the Local Planning Authority. The approved
DSMP shall be fully implemented, unless otherwise agreed in writing
by the Local Planning Authority in consultation with TfL. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that all aspects of the development to which
occupiers and /or members of the public will have access are
adequately and appropriately managed, maintained and controlled and
to minimise any potential impacts on the road network.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;span style=&quot;font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal;&quot;&gt;The
cycle storage facilities for the development hereby permitted shall
be installed prior to the first occupation of the development hereby
approved.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that a reasonable provision is made within the site
for the parking of cycles and in the interest of promoting
sustainable transport.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Prior to the occupation of the D1 space a management plan shall be
submitted to and agreed in writing by the Local Planning Authority.
Details provided in the management plan shall include, but not be
limited to: a) Maximum number of patrons b) Schedule of activities c)
Information around noise and management of such. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure the operation of the D1 space hereby approved does
not unacceptable impact neighbouring amenity.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;The development hereby permitted shall not be occupied until a site
travel welcome pack, which encourages the use of alternative modes of
transport from the private car, has been submitted to, and approved
in writing by, the local planning authority. The Welcome Pack shall
be given to all initial occupiers of the development and made
available to future occupiers on demand. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: In order to promote sustainable modes of transport.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Prior to occupation of any part of the development all of the
disabled car parking spaces proposed shall be fitted with active
electric vehicle charging points and these shall permanently remain
and be maintained for such use. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To promote sustainable modes of transport and reduce
pollution, in line with London Plan Policy 6.13&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Prior to occupation of the development, evidence (including as-built
drawings, photographs, post construction surveys) and a final
completion statement signed off by an appropriate, qualified,
indemnified engineer should be submitted showing that the sustainable
drainage system has been constructed as per the approved designs and
in accordance with best practice. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure the satisfactory completion of the SuDs system.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Prior to the occupation of the development the applicant is to submit
the following information and certification with regards to
installation to the Local Planning Authority for Approval in writing:
a) PV system with an efficiency of at least 19.4% and with an
installed area of 62.2m2 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the proposed sustainability measures are
implemented to a satisfactory standard as proposed.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Prior to occupation green / biodiverse roofs shall be installed in
full accordance with details approved as part of application
2020/2248 dated 28/08/20 and shall be retained and maintained in this
condition thereafter. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To enhance the character and ecology of the development, to
provide undisturbed refuges for wildlife, to promote sustainable
urban drainage, and to enhance the performance and efficiency of the
proposed building.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;The D1 space at Lower Ground Floor hereby permitted shall be used as
an adult study centre and for no other purpose within Use Class D1 of
the Town and Country Planning (Use Classes Order) 1987, as amended,
or in any provision equivalent to that Class in any statutory
instrument revoking and reenacting that Order. The development hereby
permitted shall not be used as a school. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the space is operated in a satisfactory
manner, does not unduly disturb adjoining occupiers, prejudice local
amenity generally as assessed in granting permission.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Prior to occupation, a Parking, Design and Management Plan shall be
submitted which should include blue badge car parking provision and
indicating how the blue badge car parking will be designed and
managed, with reference to Transport for London guidance on car
parking management and car parking design and the results of the
intrusive root survey for the adjacent TPO tree. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To promote acceptable management of vehicle parking in
association with the development.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;No vegetation at the site shall be cleared during the bird nesting
season (March to September) unless under the supervision of a
suitably qualified ornithologist and no nesting birds or their nests
shall be disturbed. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To safeguard any nesting birds and to comply with the
Wildlife and Countryside Act 1981.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;The housing mix of the development hereby approved shall be 2 x 1
bed, 8 x 2 bed and 6 x 3 bed flats, unless otherwise agreed in
writing by the local planning authority. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure the housing mix is acceptable.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;As shown on the approved drawings the lower panes of the windows and
balcony screens serving the rear elevation facing the residential
units on Overlea Road shall be fitted out with obscure glazing and
sealed shut. These details shall be maintained permanently for the
lifetime of the development. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To protect the visual privacy of the occupiers of the houses
to the rear of the site.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Two of the proposed residential units shall be built to meet building
regulations Part M4 (3), and the remaining shall be built to meet
building regulations PartM4 (2). In the interests of housing choice,
the two Part M4 (3) units shall not be of the same bedroom and person
size. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure the standard of accommodation is acceptable.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;Except on days of collection, all refuse and waste shall be stored in
sealed containers in the refuse area shown on the plans hereby
approved. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To safeguard the character and appearance of the area and in
the interests of neighbouring amenity and highway safety.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;The development shall provide level access from the public realm to
the permitted D1 space. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: In the interest of good accessibility for all users&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;No externally fixed roller shutters shall be installed to the
building hereby approved, unless otherwise agreed in writing by the
Local Planning Authority. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the external appearance of the building is
satisfactory and does not detract from the character and visual
amenity of the area.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;No new plumbing, pipes, soil stacks, flues, vents grilles, security
alarms or ductwork shall be fixed on the external faces of the
building unless as otherwise shown on the drawings hereby approved. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure that the external appearance of the building is
satisfactory and does not detract from the character and visual
amenity of the area.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;No satellite antenna, apparatus or plant of any sort (including
structures or plant in connection with the use of telecommunication
systems or any electronic communications apparatus) shall be erected
on the site or roof hereby approved unless or until details of their
size and location have previously been submitted to, for approval in
writing by the Local Planning Authority. 
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
&lt;br&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;

&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;western&quot; align=&quot;left&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0cm; line-height: 100%&quot;&gt;
REASON: To ensure a satisfactory standard of external appearance and
to protect local amenity.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

